<div id="article-header">

                


    
        	    





		
										

        


                


	    

	






 	
     	
 	
 	<div id="main-article-info">
 		
					
				
			<h1
																									>Why exercise won't make you thin</h1>
				
					<p id="stand-first"
				 class="stand-first-alone"																				>Got a few pounds to lose? Cancel the gym membership. An increasing body of research reveals that exercise does next to nothing for you when it comes to losing weight. A result for couch potatoes, yes, but also one that could have serious implications for the government's long-term health strategy</p>
		
				
  	</div>
  	
