				<h1>Why exercise won't make you thin</h1>
		   		    			    									   	This article appeared  on p28 of the <a href=http://www.guardian.co.uk/theobserver/2010/sep/19/magazine  >Observer Magazine</a> section of 					   	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theobserver"  >the Observer</a>
					   	on <time datetime="2010-09-19" pubdate><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theobserver/2010/sep/19">Sunday 19 September 2010</a></time>.
					   	It was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2010-09-19T00:00BST" pubdate>00.05 BST on Sunday 19 September 2010</time>.
